init_text: You're Barack Obama. 4 years into your retirement, you awake to find a letter with no return address on your bedside table. It reads "I hope you've had a chance to relax Barack...but pack your bags and call the number below. It's time to start the real job." Signed simply, "JFK."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He picked up the phone and dialed the number.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: , there was no voice, just a soft beeping.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You wake up in the back of a limo, and you're not alone.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: And they're all smiling at you.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: But the Secret Service agents had already grabbed you.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: No, not you, but a strange looking alien, with a strange looking face.
